import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Container, Link } from '@mui/material';
import { LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram } from '@mui/icons-material';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ bgcolor: '#1B2A44', color: '#FFFFFF', py: 6 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, mb: 2 }}>
          Hono Technology
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
          5900 Balcones Dr #16790, Austin, Texas 78731 |{' '}
          <Link href="tel:+17372390920" color="inherit" underline="hover">
            +1 737-239-0920
          </Link>{' '}
          |{' '}
          <Link href="mailto:Hr@honotech.com" color="inherit" underline="hover">
            Hr@honotech.com
          </Link>
        </Typography>
        <Box sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
          <Link href="/" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            Home
          </Link>
          <Link href="/services/app-development" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            Services
          </Link>
          <Link href="/about" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            About
          </Link>
          <Link href="/contact" color="inherit" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            Contact
          </Link>
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
          <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/honotechnology/" color="inherit" target="_blank" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            <LinkedIn />
          </Link>
          <Link href="https://facebook.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            <Facebook />
          </Link>
          <Link href="https://instagram.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" sx={{ mx: 1 }}>
            <Instagram />
          </Link>
        </Box>
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ fontWeight: 400 }}>
          Â© 2023 Hono Technology. All rights reserved.
        </Typography>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
